methods.name: createVault
methods.desc:
Create and initialize the vault
Called once at deployment

methods.name: optInAssets
methods.desc:
Opt the contract into all required assets
Must be called by creator after deployment with:
- 5.5 ALGO payment (stays in contract for MBR and operational fees)

methods.name: optIn
methods.desc: User opts into the contract to enable local storage

methods.name: closeOut
methods.desc: User closes out - claims all pending yield and withdraws all deposits first

methods.name: deposit

args.name: slippageBps
args.desc: - Slippage tolerance for auto-swap (ignored if no swap needed)

methods.desc:
User deposits Alpha into the vault
Expects an asset transfer in the group before this call

If USDC balance >= threshold and has existing depositors, automatically
swaps yield BEFORE processing deposit. This ensures yield goes to
existing depositors, not the new one.

methods.name: withdraw
methods.desc: User withdraws Alpha from the vault

methods.name: claim
methods.desc: User claims their accumulated yield (in swap_asset)

methods.name: claimCreator
methods.desc: Creator claims their accumulated yield

methods.name: swapYield
methods.desc:
Swaps accumulated USDC to project ASA via Tinyman V2
Uses ON-CHAIN price calculation - reads pool reserves and fee dynamically
Permissionless - anyone can trigger, slippage capped by maxSlippageBps

methods.name: getVaultStats
methods.desc: Get vault statistics

methods.name: getPendingYield
methods.desc: Get user's pending yield (without claiming)

methods.name: getUserDeposit
methods.desc: Get user's deposit balance

methods.name: getSwapQuote
methods.desc:
Preview swap output - shows expected ASA for current USDC balance
Reads pool state on-chain to calculate expected output

methods.name: updateMinSwapThreshold
methods.desc: Update the minimum swap threshold

methods.name: updateMaxSlippage
methods.desc:
Update the maximum slippage tolerance for swaps
Only callable by creator

methods.name: updateTinymanPool
methods.desc:
Update Tinyman pool configuration
Use only if the pool needs to be changed (e.g., migration)

methods.name: updateCreatorFeeRate
methods.desc:
Update the creator fee rate
Only callable by creator, constrained to 0-6% range

methods.name: contributeFarm
methods.desc:
Anyone can contribute to the farm by sending swapAsset
Farm bonus is distributed proportionally during yield swaps
This allows projects/sponsors to boost yield for depositors

Expects an asset transfer of swapAsset before this call

methods.name: setFarmEmissionRate

args.name: emissionRateBps
args.desc:
- Emission rate in basis points (e.g., 1000 = 10%, 5000 = 50%)
  Maximum 10000 (100%) - matches swap output 1:1
  Minimum 1000 (10%) when farm has balance (to protect contributors)

methods.desc:
Set the farm emission rate (percentage of swap output to add from farm)
Only callable by creator or RareFi

methods.name: getFarmStats
methods.desc: Get farm statistics
